&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/6LLEP3RsCoh5eujI.png!thumbnail&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;fig:&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
